---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CategoryGrid from '../components/CategoryGrid.astro';
---

<Layout title="台灣知識庫" description="開源、AI-friendly 的台灣完整知識庫，讓全世界認識真正的台灣">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <div class="taiwan-silhouette"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">Taiwan.md</h1>
      <h2 class="hero-subtitle">讓全世界完整認識台灣</h2>
      <p class="hero-description">
        開源、AI-friendly 的台灣知識庫<br>
        從歷史文化到當代生活，策展式的深度內容
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#categories" class="btn-cta primary">開始探索</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/frank890417/taiwan-md" target="_blank" class="btn-cta secondary">
          <span>⭐</span> GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">12+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">主要面向</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">100+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">預計文章</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">雙語</span>
          <span class="stat-label">中英對照</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cover-story">
    <div class="cover-content">
      <h2>如何理解台灣？</h2>
      <p class="cover-lead">
        台灣是一座面積只有 36,000 平方公里的島嶼，卻裝著整個世界的複雜度。<br>
        四百年來，每一個踏上這座島嶼的人，都用不同的眼睛看見不同的台灣。
      </p>

      <div class="quotes-timeline">
        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">原住民族</span>
          <blockquote>
            「山川河流都是祖先的身體，我們是大地的孩子。」
            <cite>— 泰雅族口傳文學</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">1584</span>
          <blockquote>
            「Isla Hermosa」— 美麗諸島。
            <cite>— 西班牙文獻，最早以「美麗」稱呼台灣的確切記錄</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">1697</span>
          <blockquote>
            「水沙連內山，山盡處有大潭，廣可數十里。中有嶼，番人聚居之。」
            <cite>— 郁永河《裨海紀遊》，清朝文人的第一手台灣觀察</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">1926</span>
          <blockquote>
            「勇士當為義鬥爭！」
            <cite>— 賴和〈覺悟下的犧牲〉，台灣新文學之父</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">1946</span>
          <blockquote>
            「台灣人的悲哀，在於不知道自己是誰。」
            <cite>— 吳濁流《亞細亞的孤兒》</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">2013</span>
          <blockquote>
            「看見台灣，你會發現，這片土地比你想像的更美麗，也比你想像的更脆弱。」
            <cite>— 齊柏林《看見台灣》</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="quote-era">
          <span class="era-label">今天</span>
          <blockquote>
            「海浪的記憶比人長。」
            <cite>— 夏曼·藍波安《天空的眼睛》，達悟族海洋文學</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cover-closing">
        <p>
          從南島語族的創世到半導體帝國的崛起，從戒嚴的沉默到亞洲第一個同婚合法化。
          台灣的故事不是一條直線，而是一張網。
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Taiwan.md 不是要給你答案。</strong>
          我們想做的，是給你一張地圖——一張讓你自己走進台灣的地圖。
        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="cover-link">閱讀完整引言集 →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <h2 class="section-title">為什麼需要 Taiwan.md？</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
        <h3>策展式內容</h3>
        <p>不是百科全書，而是精心策展的深度內容。三層閱讀深度設計，適合不同需求。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">🤖</div>
        <h3>AI-Friendly</h3>
        <p>結構化內容設計，讓 AI 也能理解台灣。促進跨文化理解與知識傳播。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">🌍</div>
        <h3>國際視野</h3>
        <p>中英雙語，從在地觀點出發，用國際語言說台灣故事。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">📚</div>
        <h3>完整性</h3>
        <p>涵蓋歷史、地理、文化、美食等 12+ 面向，呈現台灣的完整面貌。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="categories" id="categories">
    <h2 class="section-title">探索台灣</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">選擇您感興趣的面向，開始深入了解台灣</p>
    <CategoryGrid />
  </section>

  <section class="contribute">
    <div class="contribute-content">
      <h2>加入我們</h2>
      <p>Taiwan.md 是社群驅動的開源專案。無論您是台灣本地人還是對台灣感興趣的國際朋友，都歡迎貢獻您的知識與觀點。</p>
      <div class="contribute-buttons">
        <a href="/contributing" class="btn btn-primary">貢獻指南</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/your-username/taiwan-md" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank">
          GitHub 專案
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 50%, #334155 100%);
    color: white;
    margin: -2rem -1rem 0;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .taiwan-silhouette {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 40%;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1) 0%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.05) 50%, transparent 100%);
  }
  
  .taiwan-silhouette::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 60px;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(ellipse 200px 40px at 20% 100%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 150px 30px at 50% 100%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 180px 35px at 80% 100%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  
  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  
  .hero-title {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #fbbf24, #f59e0b, #dc2626);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3);
  }
  
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }
  
  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .btn-cta {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
  }
  
  .btn-cta.primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626, #b91c1c);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.3);
  }
  
  .btn-cta.primary:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b91c1c, #991b1b);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.4);
  }
  
  .btn-cta.secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }
  
  .btn-cta.secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .stat {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #fbbf24;
  }
  
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #1f2937;
  }
  
  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: #6b7280;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  .features {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  
  .feature {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }
  
  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .feature h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #1f2937;
  }
  
  .feature p {
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .categories {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  .contribute {
    background: #f9fafb;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    margin: 4rem -1rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }
  
  .contribute-content h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #1f2937;
  }
  
  .contribute-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  
  .contribute-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    background: #1e40af;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #1d4ed8;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  
  .btn-secondary {
    background: white;
    color: #1e40af;
    border: 2px solid #1e40af;
  }
  
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: #1e40af;
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }
    
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .hero-cta {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .btn-cta {
      width: 80%;
      max-width: 250px;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    
    .hero-stats {
      gap: 1.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .contribute-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }

  /* Cover Story */
  .cover-story {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: #fafbfc;
  }
  .cover-content {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .cover-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: #1a1a2e;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .cover-lead {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .quotes-timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 3rem;
  }
  .quotes-timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0.75rem;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #e2e8f0, #3b82f6, #e2e8f0);
  }
  .quote-era {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .quote-era::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -2.35rem;
    top: 0.5rem;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    background: #3b82f6;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px #3b82f6;
  }
  .era-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: #3b82f6;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .quote-era blockquote {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #334155;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .quote-era cite {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-style: normal;
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }
  .cover-closing {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #475569;
  }
  .cover-closing strong { color: #1a1a2e; }
  .cover-closing p { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cover-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    color: #3b82f6;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .cover-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>